### Implementation Details

The Analytics component is properly integrated in the root layout:

**File: `app/layout.tsx`**
- Import statement (line 6): `import { Analytics } from "@vercel/analytics/next";`
- Component placement (line 91): `<Analytics />` placed at the end of the `<body>` tag
