## Next Steps for User

To see analytics data:
1. Deploy the project to Vercel
2. Navigate to the Analytics section in the Vercel dashboard
3. Click "Enable" if not already enabled
4. Wait for user visits to accumulate
5. Check the browser Network tab for requests to `/<unique-path>/view` to verify tracking is working
